+%package glances-common
+Summary:        Glances common files (including server mode)
+Group:          System/Daemons
+Requires:       %{name} = %{version}
+%systemd_ordering
+
+%description glances-common
+This package contains common files for Glances, including the systemd
+service file for running Glances in server mode. The server allows
+remote monitoring via HTTP/HTTPS.
+
+%post glances-common
+%service_add_post glances-server.service
+
+%preun glances-common
+%service_del_preun glances-server.service
+
+%postun glances-common
+if [ $1 -ge 1 ]; then
+  %service_del_postun glances-server.service
+fi
+
